author: adrianc
msg: Fixed a design flaw in the user preference services. The services accepted an optional parameter - userLoginId - so that admins could perform CRUD operations on other user's preferences. This parameter caused a name clash with screens and services that also had a userLoginId parameter. The preference services userLoginId parameter has been renamed to userPrefLoginId.
